            . I am a labourer. Messrs. Beddalls live in High Holborn, and are <rs id="t18280221-235-viclabel1252" type="occupation">carpenters</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-235-victim1358 t18280221-235-viclabel1252"></join>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-235-victim1359 t18280221-235-viclabel1252"></join>. On the 13th of February, about seven o'clock in the morning, I was going to work at Mr. Turner's, about three doors from the building where the tarpauling was; that is in <placeName id="t18280221-235-crimeloc1253">Middleton-street, Clerkenwell</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280221-235-crimeloc1253" type="placeName" value="Middleton-street, Clerkenwell"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18280221-235-crimeloc1253" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-235-off1250 t18280221-235-crimeloc1253"></join>. I saw the prisoner coming out of the building, with it on his shoulder, and I stopped him; it was about three or four yards of old tarpauling - he said he was going home with it: he did not say where he lived, or that he worked for Beddall's.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280221-235-person1361">
                  WILLIAM 
                  TAYLOR
               <interp inst="t18280221-235-person1361" type="surname" value="TAYLOR"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280221-235-person1361" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280221-235-person1361" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I work for Messrs. Beddalls - their names are Joseph and Philip; I worked for them in Middleton-street; I left the tarpauling nailed up the night before, when I left work at half-past six o'clock. The prisoner is a stranger.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280221-235-person1362">
                  JOSEPH 
                  COOMBES
               <interp inst="t18280221-235-person1362" type="surname" value="COOMBES"></interp>
