                     <interp inst="t18280221-235-person1362" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. The prisoner was delivered over to me - he said he had found the tarpauling in the building.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going by the building, and went in for a necessary purpose; I saw the tarpauling laying, and I took it up; the place was all open.</p>
